{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1b265b1ea1","title":"给彭雪枫的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f23f3a9c3f","index":0,"year":1936,"month":10,"day":22,"articleId":"1b265b1ea1"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c7d9ab63ea","type":"paragraph","text":"给彭雪枫的信！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"1b265b1ea1"},{"id":"253e3bf4ce","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年10月22日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"1b265b1ea1"},{"id":"67476cc5d4","type":"paragraph","text":"急须将与绥普关系弄好，得信后即赴津迅速转至绥远办理此事。我有付南汉宸一信，要求他介绍你见傅作义","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"1b265b1ea1"},{"id":"9e40936048","type":"paragraph","text":"交涉要诚愿，要机警，要有耐性。专作上层交际，不与党的组织相关涉，不要引人见疑。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"1b265b1ea1"},{"id":"05ac6a14a9","type":"paragraph","text":"如傅回同意，待绥远办好后，请傅介绍见图，不同意则医，你的工作以傅为主","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"1b265b1ea1"},{"id":"57967d0e23","type":"paragraph","text":"用费从带去之四百元中升支，十分节省用，不要爱奢华，不要失掉我们的立场，不要接受人家的馈赠，只有在万不得已时，才许可从人家借一点钱，日后如数归还，用数要报账。有闲工夫注意看书报，加紧学习","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"1b265b1ea1"},{"id":"3f9ba4a967","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东致彭雪枫信的主要内容。[2]傅，指傅作义。131阁，指阁锡山。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"1b265b1ea1"}],"page":{"id":"43dd9318f4","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"1b265b1ea1","start":249,"end":249}}}},"__N_SSG":true}